ain Neutral Spirits National Distillers Products Corp New Yorir Wrangell Transfer OIL DELIVERY Office Phone _98 Home Phone_ 95 Grel HaufngGeneral Tranafp PHONT 93 with a value of 20419975 were written during the year This compares with 8064 with a value of 19110246 in 1947 In 1945 5362 money orders were written with a value of approximately 124000 A total of 2800 CODs were handled compared to 2035 in 1947 Airmail continued to show a big increase as it has yearly since its inauguration in 1945 A total of IS987 pounds of airmail was re"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-05-22T12:56:50.303Z", "group": ["ndnp/ak", "alaska-state-library-historical-collections-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn94050093/1949-02-11/ed-1/?sp=5", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ak:batch_ak_arcticfox_ver02:data:sn94050093:00513680156:1949021101:0114/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=401&w=299", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ak:batch_ak_arcticfox_ver02:data:sn94050093:00513680156:1949021101:0114/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=803&w=598", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ak/batch_ak_arcticfox_ver02/data/sn94050093/00513680156/1949021101/0114.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "wrangell", "alaska"], "location_city": ["wrangell"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_state": ["alaska"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["5", "3", "0", "sn94050093", "1", "8", "0000000005", "6"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn94050093"], "number_page": ["0000000005"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "5", "1", "3", "6", "8", "0", "1", "5", "6"], "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Not the Wrangell Sentinel"], "partof": ["the wran